metadata.name: Aureus Town
metadata.description:
The nocturnal piers, lacking a lighthouse but not lighting, welcome the golden town.

Material riches pale next to the gem that gives energy and vitality to the small seaside town.

They say that it is a tear of the god of the seas with which he blessed the small location.

It is characterized by having an active nightlife, the sun for its inhabitants indicates the end of the day.



Dimensions 120x120x120 - usable on criptovoxels.
includes .vox file.
